</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-24_ pf-text-1">Established in 1907, the NUJ has over a century of experience in advocating for media workers' rights.















</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-26_ pf-text-1">The NUJ runs various campaigns on press freedom, media plurality, and the protection of journalists.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-28_ pf-text-1">The NUJ offers training programmes to enhance professional skills and support continuous development.
















